casebody.data:
Pamela BRENNAN, et al., petitioners,
v.
CONCORD EFS, INC., et al. No. 13-63. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. Justice BREYER and Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
